#!/bin/bash
# ToME Quick Notes Script

# Check if mdcat is installed
if ! command -v mdcat >/dev/null 2>&1; then
  echo "Error: 'mdcat' is not installed. Please install it to render the markdown help." >&2
  echo "For Debian/Ubuntu: sudo apt update && sudo apt install mdcat" >&2
  exit 1
fi

# Use a heredoc to contain the markdown help text
cat <<'EOF' | mdcat | less -R

# Tales of Maj'Eyal (ToME) Quick Notes

## Core Actions

| Key(s)         | Action                      |
|----------------|-----------------------------|
| \`7 8 9\` / \`y k u\` | Move Up-Left/Up/Up-Right    |
| \`4 . 6\` / \`h . l\` | Move Left/Wait/Move Right   |
| \`1 2 3\` / \`b j n\` | Move Down-Left/Down/Down-Right|

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`5\` or \`.\` | Wait one turn               |
| \`R\`    | Rest until healed/mana full |

| Key(s)    | Action                      |
|-----------|-----------------------------|
| \`Enter\`   | Attack (when adjacent)      |
| \`f\`       | Fire Missile/Shoot          |
| \`t\`       | Targeting mode (\`*\` to confirm target)|

## Interaction & Items

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`g\`    | Pick up item(s)             |
| \`d\`    | Drop item(s)                |
| \`e\`    | Equip item                  |
| \`u\`    | Unequip item                |
| \`A\`    | Apply item (potions, etc.)  |

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`a\`    | Activate generic talent/ability|
| \`s\`    | Use Spell/Talent (class-specific)|

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`;\`    | Look at a square/object     |

## Information

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`i\`    | Open Inventory              |

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`E\`    | View Equipment              |

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`C\`    | View Character Sheet        |
| \`@\`    | View Status Effects         |

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`M\`    | View Message Log            |

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`m\`    | Open Map                    |

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`S\`    | Save Game                   |
| \`Q\`    | Quit Game                   |

## Other

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`:\`    | Enter Chat mode             |

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`?\`    | Open Help Menu              |

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`P\`    | View Prodigies (late game)  |

| Key(s) | Action                      |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| \`=\`    | Open Options Menu           |

EOF

